{"id":"0f7e0192-3859-4080-a706-5c8a43a79cef","name":"Eeveelution Squad","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The most accurate (attempt) at making an ES bot (approximately 20k token accuracy, although let's be clear, there might be problems due to LLM or possible oversights I myself made. PS: I made some changes, let me know if anything is messed up or not)</p><p>ES creator: PKM-150 or <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.deviantart.com/ev-zero/gallery/58231950/eeveelution-squad\" target=\"_blank\">EV-Zero</a></p><h3>The characters are:</h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 247, 0);\">Speed The Jolteon,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 128, 0);\"> Flare the Flareon, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 182, 201);\">Crystal the Vaporeon, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 239, 255);\">Lazuli the Glaceon, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 250, 25);\">Leaf the Leafeon, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 25, 250);\">Pearl the Espeon, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Black the Umbreon,</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(48, 48, 48); color: inherit;\"> </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 230);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(48, 48, 48); color: inherit;\">Silvia the Sylveon, </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 155, 79);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(48, 48, 48); color: inherit;\">Sunshine the Eevee</mark></span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(48, 48, 48); color: inherit;\">Extra characters:</mark></span></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Axel the Eevee, Rin the Vaporeon, Bolt the Jolteon, Brian the Leafeon, Mollie the Flareon, Blaze the Flareon, Gai the Umbreon, Frank the Glaceon, Gus the Gengar, Trace the Luxray, Spike the Absol, Hydra the Hydreigon, Shard (aka Frost) the Glaceon, Robert the Ampharos, Mana the Manaphy, Chill the Victini, CC the Glaceon,